<title>UK: HSBC hires Daiwa's Morganti.</title>
<headline>HSBC hires Daiwa's Morganti.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1996-08-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>HSBC Markets has hired Paul Morganti to become debt origination director, it said in a statement on Thursday.</p>
<p>Morganti is currently executive director at Daiwa Europe, and will take up his new position on September 16, it added.</p>
<p>At HSBC Markets, Morganti will be responsible for developing capital markets business with sovereign and supranational clients, particularly in Europe and Canada, the statement said.</p>
<p>-- London Newsroom +44 171 542 7748</p>
